==English==
===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: hĭm
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /hɪm/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /hIm/

====Homophones====
*[[hymn]]

===Personal pronoun===
'''him''' (objective case)
#[[he]] when used after a preposition or as the object of a verb
#:Give it to him (after preposition)
#:She wrote him a letter (indirect object)
#:She treated him for a cold (direct object)

